Package arithmea.client.event

Interface Summary
AddTermEventHandler Interface to handle the event to show the page for adding new words.
EditTermEventHandler Interface to handle the event to show the page for editing terms.
ParseTextEventHandler Interface to handle the event to show the page for parsing texts.
ShowInfoEventHandler Interface to handle the event to show info page.
ShowListEventHandler Interface to handle the event showing the list view.
ShowNumberEventHandler Interface to handle the event to show the page that compares numbers by methods.
TermDeletedEventHandler Interface to handle the event to delete words.

ShowNumberEvent Event to show the page that compares numbers by methods.
TermDeletedEvent Event to delete words.
